                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the metropolitan; a few lines (alternating with black lines) in the incipit page; a word, a few words, a line or a few lines of the incipit of the sections and subsections; words yǝbǝl, tǝbǝl, ǝgäle, ṣälot; elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numbers or their elements.</rubric>
